  "alternative_titles": "The Old Prisoner Lives in Solitude, The Aged Strongest Prisoner Survives Again Today, The Strongest Old Prisoner Survives Again Today, 老いた最強の囚人は今日も生き残る, 늙은 죄수는 고독에 산다",
